title: BBC4 Surviving Progess.avi
description:
I mainly upload programs from BBC4 and BBC Scotland, so I know that they will only appeal to a few viewers.

I do most seeding overnight, so I have no way of knowing how many take downloads, I have to depend on feedback to know whether I should continue uploading, and whether the quality of the uploads is good enough.

Please take a little time to leave some feedback on TPB, The Pirate Bay. 

And please keep seeding !!

Magic 1500/160k
